{"tid":191350,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打用緊凍枕頭","createTime":"2017-04-07T20:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T20:50:55.000Z","uid":68219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9886f1c4cffb7bdc5fab2545565e4dad708de24b","tid":191350,"uid":68219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T20:03:20.000Z","msg":"又是一個睡不著的夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係一個非常怕熱既人<br />\n近排d濕鳩天氣熱返 係完全無辦法瞓到<br />\n個枕頭濕曬 塊面焗到出疹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冷氣開唔到 瞓上格風扇又吹唔到<br />\n好撚慘<br />\n<br />\n有見及此 想買返個冷凝膠果類枕頭<br />\n冬天行ikea見過一隻400幾 唔知好唔好<br />\n想問下有無巴打熟依種枕頭 俾少少意見or討論下<br />\n一個熱既枕頭真係頂唔撚順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0016fb57836b93cd4ab4d54144553a101db56c","tid":191350,"uid":89999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T20:07:28.000Z","msg":"拎多少少整返部冷氣仲好啦"},{"pid":"b2b64e31a866f9acf32e20f66d91213093098392","tid":191350,"uid":4155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T20:11:04.000Z","msg":"用幾用就唔涼<br />\n我老母之前係cottex做拎俾我用"},{"pid":"7734b60566cf995fab40e974878683970b8d9e76","tid":191350,"uid":68219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T20:32:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拎多少少整返部冷氣仲好啦</blockquote><br />\n冷氣無問題 米飯班主唔想開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我塊面年年都要爛曬佢先開俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a1fd30d2db31e244194dd4ee2881b03e9bc832","tid":191350,"uid":89999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T20:50:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拎多少少整返部冷氣仲好啦</blockquote><br />\n冷氣無問題 米飯班主唔想開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我塊面年年都要爛曬佢先開俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />